markets.title: Will any MrBeast video get more than 100 Million views a week after upload?
markets.rules_primary: If MrBeast uploads a video that receives more than 100 Million views seven days after the upload date at 10:00 AM ET, before Oct 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This market will count the number of views on the seventh day AFTER the upload date. For example, if a video is uploaded on June 15th, then the view count will be checked at 10:00 AM ET seven days AFTER that date, on June 23rd. **Important information: This event will close On Oct 8, 2025 at 10:00am ET to encompass the case of a video being uploaded as late as Sep 30, 2025.**
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
